Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:26.35,CH-BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\3c&H0F7FDC&\fad(200,200)}所以就轻便一点 戴上兜帽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:29.29,CH-BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\3c&H0F7FDC&\fad(200,200)}小心翼翼地 出发吧
