Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:52.23,CH-BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\3c&H0F7FDC&\fad(200,200)}糟糕 又要变成如往常一般的周末了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.67,CH-BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\3c&H0F7FDC&\fad(200,200)}好累啊 好想放弃啊
